message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I can't believe the terrible service I've received from your company! My claim has been pending for weeks and I'm fed up with the lack of communication.
I'm deeply sorry to hear about your experience with us. I understand how frustrating it must be. Before we proceed further, for security purposes, can you confirm your full name?
Thank you for confirming. Can you also provide me with your date of birth for additional checks?
Great, thank you. To proceed, can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
Thank you for completing security. I truly value your feedback. Now, how can we assist you with your pending claim today?
I expect better communication and a resolution to my claim as soon as possible. This has been a nightmare.
I completely understand your frustration, John. Let's work together to find a solution. A possible resolution could be escalating your claim for urgent processing. How does that sound to you?
It's about time! Yes, that sounds like the least you could do at this point.
I'm glad we could help with that. I will make sure your claim is escalated. Is there anything else you would like us to assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. I hope this time my issue will be taken seriously.
Thank you for reaching out to us, John. Please allow 24-48 hours for the escalation to be processed. We truly value your patience and are here to help if you need anything else. Have a great day!
